	('Semolina pie (manna)','When you need simple pastries on kefir, recipes with photos, simple and tasty, come in handy. Here is a pie with semolina on kefir, very good for tea. And you can serve semolina pie for breakfast, like a casserole, with sour cream or jam. Mannik is delicious baked goods! Recipes with photos will help you prepare it.',9),
	('Cupcake "Zebra" with kefir and vegetable oil','I try to pamper my family with baked goods as often as possible - buns, pies, muffins, tortillas and pizza! Over the years, she has collected many secrets for perfect baking. Today I will share a recipe for Zebra pie with kefir and vegetable oil. Heat eggs for the most perfect result! It always turns out to be a plus!',9),
	('Khichiny with cheese and potatoes','Traditional baking recipes are simple and proven. Do you have kefir or sour milk and a piece of cheese? This dish is for you! The recipe for making khychins - Caucasian flatbreads with cheese and potatoes. The dough for thin khychins on kefir is very simple to prepare, especially since it is baked goods without eggs. You will like kefir baked goods.',9),
